00:00:00,090 --> 00:00:02,260
<i>[Drama Stream]</i>

2
00:00:02,260 --> 00:00:04,250
Hi! Good afternoon.

3
00:00:04,250 --> 00:00:08,070
If you walk spread out like that, you'll block traffic.

4
00:00:08,730 --> 00:00:10,930
What's Tetsuko's deal?

5
00:00:10,930 --> 00:00:14,660
There's no rush. You've already shook hands, after all.

6
00:00:14,660 --> 00:00:18,590
- Right.
- But it's been over a month since then and nothing happened!

7
00:00:18,590 --> 00:00:20,920
Talk about what you want!

8
00:00:20,920 --> 00:00:23,700
Like, "I want to do this", or, "I want to do that"!

9
00:00:23,700 --> 00:00:27,610
Of course, I'll do those things. This and that.

10
00:00:28,190 --> 00:00:29,410
One day.

11
00:00:29,410 --> 00:00:33,840
<i>No racing heart, shortness of breath, or dizziness. I'm finally under control.</i>

12
00:00:33,840 --> 00:00:38,130
<i>I have conquered Murai!</i>

13
00:00:38,130 --> 00:00:40,000
Good afternoon.

14
00:00:40,920 --> 00:00:43,300
Were you smiling just now?

15
00:00:44,300 --> 00:00:45,900
What?

16
00:00:46,750 --> 00:00:50,140
You were just smiling.

17
00:00:54,490 --> 00:00:57,550
So you're capable of smiling too.

18
00:01:00,150 --> 00:01:02,530
<i>Summer vacation, right?</i>

19
00:01:02,530 --> 00:01:05,690
Even if they force you to attend extra lessons, it's only for a few days.

20
00:01:05,690 --> 00:01:07,640
That's true.

21
00:01:07,640 --> 00:01:12,080
You'll have endure not being able to see Tetsuko for over a month.

22
00:01:13,020 --> 00:01:14,410
Wait, where is Hirai?

23
00:01:14,410 --> 00:01:17,880
Hirai is in trouble with a group of girls.

24
00:01:17,880 --> 00:01:20,270
Again?

25
00:01:21,070 --> 00:01:23,200
Well, see you tomorrow.

26
00:01:23,200 --> 00:01:25,740
- Bye bye.
- Bye bye.

27
00:01:27,860 --> 00:01:29,770
Chi-chan!

28
