Yayo-chan?

30
00:01:38,570 --> 00:01:41,180
<i>I asked your family, and they said you were still at school.</i>

31
00:01:41,180 --> 00:01:43,210
I couldn't wait, so I came looking for you.

32
00:01:43,210 --> 00:01:44,660
Did I bother you?

33
00:01:44,660 --> 00:01:46,020
Not at all.

34
00:01:46,020 --> 00:01:48,010
How's your family? Is everyone well?

35
00:01:48,010 --> 00:01:49,970
Of course.

36
00:01:51,740 --> 00:01:53,260
Did something happen?

37
00:01:53,260 --> 00:01:54,830
What?

38
00:01:54,830 --> 00:01:58,900
Your hair. I thought you had long hair, so I was surprised.

39
00:01:58,900 --> 00:02:00,950
Kind of.

40
00:02:00,950 --> 00:02:03,570
Why did you visit my house, Yayo-chan?

41
00:02:04,230 --> 00:02:06,420
"Why"?

42
00:02:07,080 --> 00:02:10,720
I came to see you, Chi-chan.

43
00:02:14,560 --> 00:02:17,990
I did my best.

44
00:02:20,730 --> 00:02:23,590
<i>- Hey! Don't run away, Hirai!
- Stop running!</i>

45
00:02:23,590 --> 00:02:27,960
- <i>I said I was sorry!
- I will make sure you never touch a girl again!</i>

46
00:02:27,960 --> 00:02:30,930
That's Hirai! I'm sorry. They're chasing my friend.

47
00:02:30,930 --> 00:02:32,030
What?

48
00:02:32,030 --> 00:02:34,320
See you later, Yayo-chan.

49
00:02:38,390 --> 00:02:40,900
He cares about his friends...

50
00:02:41,990 --> 00:02:46,400
<i>He's never changed. He's such a kind guy.</i>

51
00:02:49,010 --> 00:02:51,780
Could you guys cut it out?

52
00:02:52,920 --> 00:02:54,820
I love him!

53
00:02:58,220 --> 00:03:00,560
End of term. End of term. Then you'll be in heaven.

54
00:03:00,560 --> 00:03:04,240
You'll hole up in your room, just you and Hitotose. End of term-

55
00:03:04,240 --> 00:03:06,880
What are you mumbling about?

56
00:03:09,730 --> 00:03:12,610
A work matter. I can't forget about it.

57
00:03:12,610 --> 00:03:17,540
Really? I wish you would think about Murai with that kinda enthusiasm.

58
00:03:20,990 --> 00:03:23,770
I am grateful for your advice.

59
00:03:23,770 --> 00:03:26,530
I was able to face him because of it,

60
00:03:26,530 --> 00:03:29,080
and preserve the line between teacher and student.

61
00:03:29,080 --> 00:03:30,820
What more do you want me to do?

62
00:03:30,820 --> 00:03:33,430
I want to know one thing.

63
00:03:33,430 --> 00:03:35,610
The person you like is a character from a video game-

64
00:03:35,610 --> 00:03:38,670
Quiet! Someone could hear!

65
00:03:39,460 --> 00:03:42,480
- Why do you like Hitotose?
- What?

66
00:03:42,480 --> 00:03:46,600
What made you like him? It wasn't his looks, right?

67
00:03:47,520 --> 00:03:49,500
Goodbye.

68
00:03:50,600 --> 00:03:52,890
Stingy!

69
00:03:53,900 --> 00:03:56,070
I can just tell...

70
00:03:56,070 --> 00:03:58,120
She's like us.

